Sentencas: The (La,Sr) (Co, Fe)O3-delta(LSCF)/YSZ and LSCF/GDC composite cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC) were prepared by the impregnation method and screen printing method, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performance of (La,Sr) (Co,Fe)O3-δ Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The cathodes were characterized by X-ray diffraction, scanning electron microscopy, and electrochemical impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performance of (La,Sr) (Co,Fe)O3-δ Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results indicated that no new phase was formed in the LSCF/YSZ electrode after calcination at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performance of (La,Sr) (Co,Fe)O3-δ Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Under the working temperature of 700-750 degrees C, the LSCF cathode prepared by impregnation showed good chemical compatibility with YSZ and high electrocatalytic activity for O-2 reduction, while the LSCF cathode prepared by screen printing showed stable electrocatalytic performance under polarization current.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performance of (La,Sr) (Co,Fe)O3-δ Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
